com.podevs.android.poAndroid

Class ProtocolVersion

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.podevs.android.poAndroid.ProtocolVersion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SerializeBytes

    public class ProtocolVersion
extends java.lang.Object
implements SerializeBytes
    Describes the protocol version of the client or server. Protocol versions have a major version(version) and a minor version (minorVersion), that both range from 0 to 65536. Use compareTo to compare two protocol versions.
